divs: Sighting DetailsDriving north from Walkerton Ontario towards Chesley on CR19. Looked to the west and seen a bright white star-like object pulsating with 3 smaller objects directly underneath it. The middle object was red. To the north of the object was a triangle of lights and the one corner pulsated approximately every 10 seconds. There also was another object pulsating close to the triangle formation. After watching it for 5 minutes, the object with the 3 smaller objects underneath it moved left, then move right very slowly.
